text: Scinax iquitorum is a frog. It lives in Peru. Scientists have seen it near Río Nanay and Río Yavari. This frog is light green on the back with bright yellow color on its sides. It has black spots. The backs of its back legs are black. The iris of its eye is gold or the color of bronze. ==References== Category:Frogs of South America
title: Scinax iquitorum
